{
  "stem": "3341.2",
  "chunk_idx": 17,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my father-- we had-- we had a very big country-- like, a townhouse, a big one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the entrance was like here, but with gates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "No, the entrance was like in a passage, because in the front was one of our shops, one of our businesses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So there was a side entrance to the building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the side entrance to the actual flat, we had lot of staircase, like winding staircase.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a baroque style house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And to make it safe, when these tragic times started, my father installed a steel gate, which is, like, shutters, you know, which you-- like harmonica shutters, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "During the day, it was open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "For the night, they always locked it, and put even the lock there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they came that particular night, I don't even know which day or which month it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came and wanted to collect us and the parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was already up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was two o'clock, I think, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They banged on the steel gate, open up, open up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father pushed my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had on the top floor, not a secret passage, like a little staircase, inside staircase, leading to the roof, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father forced my mother to-- she was only in the nightie, dressing gown-- or she put the dressing gown on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, you go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Go upstairs and hide anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hide behind, because we had huge chimneys there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the roof, was like, so big, like this room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Every section of it was like a separate room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We used to dry clothes in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
